    @{b}HOTLIST@{ub} args

        args can be:

            o ADD
              Add the current module to the hotlist

              RETURNS
                RC=0 if success
                RC=1 if an error occurs (i.e no module loaded)


            o SAVE
              Saves the hotlist

              RETURNS
                RC = 0 if success
                RC = 1 if failure

            o OPEN
              Open the hotlist window


            o CLOSE
              Close the hotlist-window


            o EDIT [CLOSE]

              Opens the edit-hotlist window

              If CLOSE argument is used,
              the window will be closed

        

