@node ware "Postcard ware"

    (¯`·._.·' Showmodule GUI Mega Webber `·._.·'¯)


             (_.·'¯ POSTCARDWARE ¯`·._)


If you like this program it'd be nice of you
to send me a postcard from where you are!!!

I will problably make a list of users on the
homapage, and also in the future manuals.

So if you send me a postcard, you will be added
to the list (if you want to) and other users
will be able to get to know you.

The postcard shall not be a "electronic" one,
but a real one! You can find my address at
the @{"author" link author} part in this manual.

And since I love getting postcards, this will be
the only way to get on the list :)

@endnode

